OL,4,Cas filming for 28 Days Later sequel
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FA host of Hollywood stars have
OL,8,Fdescended on Northumberland for
OL,9,Ffilming on the sequel of 28 Days Later.
OL,11,FJodie Comer and award-winning film
OL,12,Fmaker Danny Boyle were among those in
OL,13,FRothbury for the shoot for 28 years
OL,14,FLater - the film that will be set 28
OL,15,Fyears after the original.
OL,17,FComer was seen walking around the
OL,18,FSimonside Hills trying to hide from
OL,19,Fthe cameras while dressed in costume.
OL,20,FMeanwhile, Boyle was later spotted
OL,21,Fqueuing for the catering van.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
