OL,4,Cas filming for 28 Days Later sequel
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,FHowever, the duo were overshadowed by
OL,8,Fsome particularly woolly sheep. The
OL,9,Fanimals were dressed in giant fleeces
OL,10,Fto make give them the appearance of
OL,11,Fbeing unsheared on camera.
OL,13,FBoyle spoke to local councillor Steven
OL,14,FBridgett during the shoot on the
OL,15,Fhills, telling him how much he had
OL,16,Fenjoyed filming in Rothbury and
OL,17,FNorthumberland so far.
OL,19,F"We've had a great time in Rothbury,"
OL,20,Fhe said. "We got a camera down there
OL,21,Fwith very woolly sheep.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
