OL,3,CJodie Comer and Danny Boyle pictured
OL,4,Cas filming for 28 Days Later sequel
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,F"Try to imagine what sheep are like if
OL,8,Fthey haven't been shorn.
OL,10,F"We have been up on the hillside which
OL,11,Fis absolutely beautiful. It's a
OL,12,Fwonderful place to come and film, the
OL,13,Fwhole of Northumberland but Rothbury
OL,14,Fis particularly nice."
OL,16,FThe film shoots have brought an extra
OL,17,Fbuzz to the town with residents trying
OL,18,Fto catch a glimpse of the Hollywood
OL,19,Fstars.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
