OL,7,F"The excitement has been building
OL,8,Fsince we received letters a few weeks
OL,9,Fago that they were coming," said Neil
OL,10,FLafferty. "I am a big fan of the film
OL,11,Fso obviously I was a little bit
OL,12,Foverexcited.
OL,14,F"To be right outside, on this road
OL,15,Fwith an oscar winning director is a
OL,16,Fbit surreal. I opened up the curtains
OL,17,Fthis morning and saw Danny Boyle
OL,18,Foutside my window. I couldn't get
OL,19,Fdressed quick enough to get outside.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
