OL,4,Cas filming for 28 Days Later sequel
OL,5,Cbegins
OL,7,F"He's lovely. He's really nice. The
OL,8,Fcrew have all said how friendly and
OL,9,Famiendable he is and how he wants to
OL,10,Fmeet people all the time. But for him
OL,11,Fto take time and speak to us and a
OL,12,Fcouple over the road as well, really
OL,13,Fnice bloke."
OL,15,FIt is also hoped the filming will help
OL,16,Fprovide a boost to the area as the
OL,17,Ffilm crews visit local businesses.
