OL,7,F"You have got some of the crew staying
OL,8,Fwithin the village and using local
OL,9,Ffacilities for food and drink,"
OL,10,Fexplained Councillor Bridgett. "You
OL,11,Fhave also got the fact it is going to
OL,12,Fbe in a movie which is a great
OL,13,Fadvertisement for the local area as
OL,14,Fwell."
